Debo, popular skit maker and comedian known as Mr Macaroni, has publicly praised Davido’s father for his kindness towards him while he was in school in recent tweets. 

He revealed that Davido’s father,  Dr Deji Adeleke, is a great giver and he learnt to give and help others from the older Adeleke.


He added that Davido’s father bought him his first laptop when he got admission into the university and was always available whenever he needed help financially.


